                <p class="label">Castle Escape</p>
                <p class="summary">&quot;The Princess was kidnapped by the Monster King. And the hero sent to save her… won’t be able to do much. Gaining a once in a lifetime opportunity, the Princess has killed the Monster King and stole his weapons. Now armed, she must battle her way down the castle’s floors in order to escape the henchmen who are not going to sit idle. React fast and outsmart your enemies as the Princess in order to make your own happy ending. But the longer you take, the less chance you have of leaving before you are overwhelmed by the guards.&quot;</p>
                
